ddu_SIC (&506E1)
{f25}Þ{f}	R0 =	Window handle
		R1 =	Icon handle
		R2 =	Foreground colour
		R3 =	<Background colour=>.bgcol>
{f25}Ü{f}	All registers preserved
Not re-entrant.
#line
Set an icon's colour
#line
*Basic example*:
#fCode;indent 4;wrap off
SYS "ddu_SIC",Window,Icon,7,11
#wrap;indent;f
#
#subpage bgcol
ddu_SIC Background colour
If R3 =	0..15	the icon gets a filled background
If R3 =	-1	the icon background gets transparent
